  "parts": [
    {
      "id": "l2-worker-statistics",
      "title": "Worker Statistics",
      "prompt": "Extend the register with rankings. All Level 1 operations keep working.\n\n**New operation**\n\n- `[\"TOP_N_WORKERS\", n, position]` — return up to `n` workers whose **current** position is `position`, formatted as `workerId(time)`, joined by commas. Sort by total completed time worked in that position descending, then by worker id ascending. Include matching workers with zero completed time if there are not enough non-zero workers. Return `\"\"` if `n` is `0` or no worker currently has that position.",
      "tests": [
        {
          "name": "l2-ranks-workers-by-time",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "ADD_WORKER",
                "Ann",
                "engineer",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "ADD_WORKER",
                "Bob",
                "engineer",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "ADD_WORKER",
                "Cyd",
                "qa",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "REGISTER",
                "Ann",
                "0"
              ],
              [
                "REGISTER",
                "Ann",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "REGISTER",
                "Bob",
                "15"
              ],
              [
                "REGISTER",
                "Bob",
                "35"
              ],
              [
                "TOP_N_WORKERS",
                "2",
                "engineer"
              ],
              [
                "TOP_N_WORKERS",
                "5",
                "qa"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "true",
            "registered",
            "registered",
            "registered",
            "registered",
            "Bob(20),Ann(10)",
            "Cyd(0)"
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l2-ties-and-empty-results",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "ADD_WORKER",
                "zoe",
                "engineer",
                "1"
              ],
              [
                "ADD_WORKER",
                "amy",
                "engineer",
                "1"
              ],
              [
                "TOP_N_WORKERS",
                "5",
                "engineer"
              ],
              [
                "TOP_N_WORKERS",
                "0",
                "engineer"
              ],
              [
                "TOP_N_WORKERS",
                "2",
                "qa"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "amy(0),zoe(0)",
            "",
            ""
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
